Italian publishers are represented with a strong field at the Frankfurt International Book Fair.
More than three hundred Italian publishing houses will be present at the most significant international copyright meeting at the 60th Buchmesse fair.
For this year's Frankfurt International Book Fair, 7,000 exhibitors from 101 countries are expected in 171.790 square meters, where more than 403.000 books will be presented.
